 ries from the Kripke collection including an 1828 Webster's dictionary an
 d slang dictionaries from the 20th century." src="https://events.iu.edu/l
 ive/image/gid/261/width/500/height/333/30107_kripke_collection_photo_2.re
 v.1771333324.png" title="kripke collection photo" data-max-w="768" data-m
