X-LIVEWHALE-CONTACT-INFO:<p>\n  <strong>Lilly Library</strong><br />\n  <
 a href="mailto:liblilly@iu.edu">liblilly@iu.edu<br />\n  <br /></a>\n</p>
X-LIVEWHALE-SUMMARY:<p>\n  See the Lilly Library's rare original copy of 
 the Declaration of Independence and learn all about it from Erika Dowell\
 , curator of the library's 2026 exhibition about the nation's founding do
 cument.\n</p>
